{"tid":47694,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]睇返新紮師兄續集，發覺以前嘅吳孟達好似冇後生過咁","createTime":"2016-12-20T13:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:41:01.000Z","uid":34701,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20c904d7b21ade843226b1bf6f85aea3f82e6d44","tid":47694,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:45:10.000Z","msg":"達哥係1952年出世，啫係拍新紥師兄續集嗰陣只係33歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn1.mmia.com/o_19vukohjqvhl1m51qaugleunn1b.jpg?watermark/1/image/aHR0cDovL2NkbjEubW1pYS5jb20vbW1pYV9tYXJrLnBuZw==/dissolve/50/gravity/SouthEast/dx/25/dy/25/auto-orient\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.mmia.com%2Fo_19vukohjqvhl1m51qaugleunn1b.jpg%3Fwatermark%2F1%2Fimage%2FaHR0cDovL2NkbjEubW1pYS5jb20vbW1pYV9tYXJrLnBuZw%3D%3D%2Fdissolve%2F50%2Fgravity%2FSouthEast%2Fdx%2F25%2Fdy%2F25%2Fauto-orient&h=c5def55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返再年輕d嘅佢<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2015/10/17/phpkUZvo6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F10%2F17%2FphpkUZvo6.jpg&h=86e7fdae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢套係1979年嘅楚留香，嗰陣佢先27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個樣真係起碼老10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家啲人成日話邊個邊個係美魔男/女，唔識老咁，但達哥就正正係一個相反，想像唔到佢BB嗰陣係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcff0e27932771756318209744a3fecf97bd74c","tid":47694,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"笑咗"},{"pid":"f05434b9d776865f85ddce78c5105a0ece961c49","tid":47694,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cea984d7ad5e2688bfbdd8d9ce811ea666309770","tid":47694,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"佢同華仔星爺差唔夠十年<br />\n但扮佢老豆係完全無違和感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3376d48d39650e9c0e3823af573082b3ce5e70","tid":47694,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢同華仔星爺差唔夠十年<br />\n但扮佢老豆係完全無違和感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以注定佢做唔到主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9456e800b7f39184f82cffc72a98b511d4ad68e7","tid":47694,"uid":944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講唔覺"},{"pid":"f6454bba5243b3936bc989de5f238e00b147ce1a","tid":47694,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"廁所達 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b17ca5767b66dad320360a5bf3b9698e1b84e2f","tid":47694,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講唔覺</blockquote><br />\n其實我都睇過無線之前重播79年版楚留香，不過冇刻意查達哥嗰陣幾多歲<br />\n近排睇返新紥師兄續集見到有佢就忍唔住去查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a557d09962c9971b3d047d98715f6a03a7b5bc","tid":47694,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"再嚟睇下1989年(37歲)嘅達哥<br />\n<img src=\"http://s6.sinaimg.cn/large/004kGfcqzy6MPu7qzvnc5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F